{"tid":190930,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"邱禮濤 X 黃秋生 血腥Cult 片《失眠》","createTime":"2017-04-07T12:42:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T06:55:55.000Z","uid":864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6869c8dd9a8d530f2f5c24baf14dcc9faa370c4","tid":190930,"uid":864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T12:42:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jb45qYllvb4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fjb45qYllvb4&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=84f83a23\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jb45qYllvb4</a><br />\n<br />\n《#失眠》<br />\n著名大學醫學院教授林惜家（黃秋生　飾），專門研究人類可以長時間不需睡眠的方法。一天，前女友丘夢熙（吳俐璇　飾）突然現身求助，原來她的家人全部患上失眠症，病情去到末期，病人更會陷入失常狀態、極具攻擊性！為探究真相，林惜家開始連串恐怖實驗：潛入停屍間偷取病人大腦，又把丘夢熙關在密室軟禁，藉此研究睡眠和大腦蛋白質之間的關係&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n隨著實驗愈深入，蹊蹺的事情不斷在丘夢熙身上發生；就連林惜家也看似受感染，心底開始出現吃人肉的慾望&hellip; 原來一切牽涉到45年前，孿生姐妹侯文媛和侯文禎（衛詩雅 分飾）的一宗倫常慘案有關！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無人期待緊uncut版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f03b80bf067b9e32ef7893f2ef196a2223e085e","tid":190930,"uid":864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7bb38c60bad95dedf18d9dcfbfeaf81991be325","tid":190930,"uid":44547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾時出uncut 版"},{"pid":"dce830f5519f9303350203cb0a912c49f3b51527","tid":190930,"uid":15045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a4255affb3ee99da6e1eb0312070be123b1418","tid":190930,"uid":864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:15:36.000Z","msg":"<a hr